<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m sure you&apos;ve read the book already Hira, but for other curious readers:<br/>In my opinion, I didn&apos;t find the book scary at all, but it is by far the mos<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm sure you've read the book already Hira, but for other curious readers:<br />In my opinion, I didn't find the book scary at all, but it is by far the most gruesome, graphic book I have ever read in my entire life. There are very graphic descriptions of skin infections and other various concerning imagery. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
