        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer232962579" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7091093872679688160">Thrilling, well told, and very, very dark. I listened to this book on Audio, and found I could not stop listening. I was still tuned in at the wee hours of the morning. I was surprised at how very dark and grotesque some of the descriptions were -- especially considering that this is a young adult novel, but the literary quality is so strong, it doesn’t detract from it. It felt like something Poe might write if he lived today.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


