        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer113695204" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14982421839813575189"><blockquote>
  <b>
    <i>Yes, my dear child, monsters are real.</i>
  </b>
</blockquote><br/><b>2.5 stars</b>. This was a perfect Halloween pick. It&apos;s really too bad I didn&apos;t read Monstrumologist in one sitting. I probably would have appreciated it more if I had. The world was inventive and the tone was deliciously spooky, which I liked. But I had trouble picking the book back up after taking a break because it read on the slower side. <br/></span>
  <span id="freeText14982421839813575189" style="display:none"><blockquote>
  <b>
    <i>Yes, my dear child, monsters are real.</i>
  </b>
